<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">You need to:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>choose one of the 6 DfE-funded training providers as soon as possible</li>
    <li>tell us each ECT and mentor’s name and email address as soon as possible</li>
    <li>have an appropriate body in place</li>
</ul>
<p class="govuk-body"><%= govuk_link_to "Read our guidance (opens in new tab)", step_by_step_path %> to find out how to complete these steps.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">You do not need to let the DfE know which provider you choose. Your training provider will contact us to arrange funding.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">You’re ready to add new ECTs and mentors</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">You must tell us their:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>full name</li>
    <li>email address</li>
</ul>
<p class="govuk-body">You can now choose to enter their teacher reference number (TRN) and date of birth too.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">If you can tell us this extra information:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-margin-bottom-7">
    <li>ECTs and mentors will not be asked to provide this information themselves</li>
    <li>we can confirm if they’re eligible for funding more quickly</li>
</ul>